The '''Kofiau monarch''' ('''''Symposiachrus julianae''''') is a species of [[bird]] in the family [[Monarchidae]]. It is [[Endemism|endemic]] to [[Kofiau]] in Indonesia.

==Taxonomy and systematics==
This species was originally classified in the genus ''[[Monarcha]]'' until moved to ''Symposiachrus'' in 2009.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.worldbirdnames.org/Archives/Master_IOC_list_v2.0.xls|title=IOC Bird List v2.0|date=2009|access-date=28 October 2016}}</ref> 

